  "description": "The second season of <i>Hataraku Saibou</i>.<br>\n<br>\nCells at Work!! continues the tale of…well…you! Set inside the human body, Cells at Work!! chronicles the life and times of everything from the oxygen-carrying Red Blood Cells to the bacteria-fighting White Blood Cells. And, of course, the dangerous viruses and villains lurking beneath the skin!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)<br>\n<br>\n<i>Notes:<br>\n- The episodes were streamed two days ahead of the Japanese broadcast on Funimation beginning on Jan 8, 2021 at 2:00 JST. The regular TV broadcast started on Jan 9, 2021 at 23:30 JST.<br>\n- The pre-screened movie <b>\"Hataraku Saibou!!\" Saikyou no Teki, Futatabi. Karada no Naka wa \"Chou\" Oosawagi!</b> is included as episodes 4-8 split into the broadcast.</i>",
